These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, disco, blues, salsa
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, documentary, animation, zombie
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
2. the fan disco is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the fan blues is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the fan dubstep is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the fan blues##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | disco   | salsa    | dubstep    | blues |
| Sport      | zombie | martial-arts | animation | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
4 different games are played: whist, domino, monopoly, mah-jongg
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, baking, hiking, writing
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
2. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5
3. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the left of the person playing mah-jongg##5
4. the person playing domino is not the person who's hobby is baking##6
5. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
8. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | domino  | monopoly    | whist | mah-jongg    |
| Food       | writing | baking | hiking  | chess |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
4 different games are played: canasta, bridge, go, mah-jongg
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, gardening, cooking, traveling
1. the person playing mah-jongg is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the person playing go##6
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person playing canasta##1
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | mah-jongg       | bridge  | canasta  | go |
| Job        | cooking | traveling | gardening | fishing  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, mystery, fantasy
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, pink, blood-red, azure
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
3. the person who likes azure is not the person watching martial-arts movies##6
4. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | martial-arts | mystery | fantasy     | zombie |
| Transport   | pink     | blood-red    | green | azure    |

