.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, june, july
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, software-developer, electrician, paramedic
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5
3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
4. the person who's birthday is in december is not the paramedic##6
5. the firefighter is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | march        | july | june | december |
| Transport   | paramedic | firefighter | software-developer     | electrician   |

