.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
House: palace, victorian, tower, cape-cod
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, indie, pop
1. the fan country is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the cape-cod house is not the fan electronic##6
3. the fan country is on the far right##1
4. the fan electronic is somewhere to the right of the fan pop##5
5. the tower house is the tower house##1
6. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the fan country##5
7. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
8. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5
9. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the fan pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | victorian | tower    | palace  | cape-cod   |
| Nationality   | indie  | pop | electronic | country |

