.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, project-manager, engineer, coach
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, indonesian, indian, brazilian
1. the indian is on the left or right of the thai##3
2. the indian is not the project-manager##6
3. the photographer is the indonesian##1
4. the thai is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
5. the indian is on the far left##1
6. the project-manager is the thai##1
7. the coach is somewhere to the left of the thai##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | coach | project-manager     | engineer | photographer |
| Music-Genre   | indian | thai | brazilian      | indonesian         |

