.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
City: new-york, london, edinburgh, nizza
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, mystery, zombie, animation
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
6. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
7. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
8. the person traveling to london is not the person watching animation movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | london  | new-york        | edinburgh      | nizza          |
| Job        | spy | mystery | animation | zombie |

