.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, dog, hamster, hedgehog
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, turquise, lilac, emerald
1. the owner of the goat is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes turquise is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
3. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
4. the person who likes emerald is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
6. the person who likes emerald is the owner of the hamster##1
7. the owner of the goat is not the person who likes emerald##6
8. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | goat  | hamster | hedgehog    | dog |
| Transport   | turquise | emerald | lilac | lavender  |

