.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, jet-ski, skateboard
There are 4 different nationalities: american, german, japanese, argentine
1. the american is not the person driving the ship##6
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the argentine is the argentine##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the argentine##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is not the argentine##6
6. the german is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
7. the argentine is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the jet-ski is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | jet-ski | ship        | skateboard  | snowmobile     |
| Sport   | american     | argentine | german | japanese |

