.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, september, april
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, pakistani, american, colombian
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
3. the american is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the colombian and the person who's birthday is in september##2
5. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
6. the pakistani is between the argentine and the person who's birthday is in november##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | september | may    | november | april |
| Music-Genre   | argentine         | pakistani | colombian   | american     |

