.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, surfing, skiing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, gospel, soul, punk
1. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the right of the fan soul##5
2. the person who's sport is skiing is not the fan pop##6
3. the fan gospel is the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the fan gospel is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the fan soul is not the person who's sport is skiing##6
6. the person who's sport is handball is not the fan pop##6
7. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | lacrosse  | surfing | handball | skiing |
