.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, juice, milk, almond-milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, alhambra, siglo, old-henry
1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
2. the person drinking juice is not the alhambra-smoker##6
3. the person drinking sprite is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
5. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking juice and the blend-smoker##2
6. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | almond-milk | juice      | sprite | milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | alhambra     | siglo | old-henry   | blend |

