There are 4 different nationalities: polish, japanese, mexican, dutch
1. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
2. the polish is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
3. the japanese is on the left of the polish##1
4. the dutch is not the person traveling to prague##6
5. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to colone##2
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | colone | marseilles | prague | san-francisco |
| Pet     | mexican  | japanese      | polish  | dutch       |

